Thumby Surf is a game similiar to the offline Edge Surf. It is designed to be minamal and able to run on the OG Thumby.

The objective is to get as far as you can and there will be a counter to track how far you went. You will try to avoid many obstacles. You have 3 hearts and once you have used your 3 hearts, you will be prompted into the end screen with the score you got and your high score. 

